<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .order-summary {
        background-color: #f0f4f8;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .order-summary h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .order-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      }
      .order-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
      <p>Thank you for your purchase! Below are the details of your order:</p>

      <div class="order-summary">
        <h2>Order Summary</h2>
        <div class="order-item">
          <span><strong>Course Name:</strong></span>
          <span>Fullstack Web Development - MERN Stack</span>
        </div>
        <div class="order-item">
          <span><strong>Order ID:</strong></span>
          <span>6864c2fb09ae62856a0b1e4f</span>
        </div>
        <div class="order-item">
          <span><strong>Price:</strong></span>
          <span>$69.67</span>
        </div>
        <div class="order-item">
          <span><strong>Date:</strong></span>
          <span>July 6, 2025</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to reach out to our
        support team.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">&copy; 2025 Learn Vista LMS. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
